1 Authority on or after that date. The modifications to appointments and term limits of members
2 of the Cherokee County Tourism Development Authority under Section 1 of this act become
3 incrementally effective upon the expiration of the terms of current members of the Authority and
4 applicable to newly seated members of the Authority thereafter.
